Para executar:
To run:
Start up.
Clear the screen.
Use medium letters. Use the fat pen. [Face northwest.]
Loop.
Pick an dark color.
Start in the center of the screen.
Turn left 1/32 of the way.
Turn right. Move 2 inches. Turn left.
Write "ацбийстуш".
Refresh the screen.
Lighten the current color about 20 percent.
Add 1 to an count. If the count is 32, break.
Repeat.
Wait por the escape key.
Shut down.


To start in the center of the screen:
Start in the center of the screen's box.